Income Tax Sappy (1954)

   Director: Jules White
   Cast: Vernon Dent, Nanette Bordeaux, Margie Liszt

   Tax cheats Moe, Larry and Shemp decide they're so good at cheating the government, that they start a business as crooked tax advisors. They become rich, but an undercover agent from the IRS gets the goods on them, and its off to jail for the Three Stooges.
